Package com.intellij.ide.structureView

Interface StructureViewModel

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Disposable, TreeModel
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    PropertiesGroupingStructureViewModel, StructureViewModel.ElementInfoProvider
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DomStructureViewTreeModel, JavaFileTreeModel, JsonStructureViewModel, PropertiesFileStructureViewModel, PyStructureViewModel, ResourceBundleStructureViewModel, RestStructureViewModel, StructureViewCompositeModel, StructureViewModelBase, TextEditorBasedStructureViewModel, TreeModelWrapper, XmlStructureViewTreeModel

    public interface StructureViewModel
extends TreeModel, Disposable
    Defines the model for the data displayed in the standard structure view or file structure popup component. The model of the standard structure view is represented as a tree of elements. Use StructureViewModel.ElementInfoProvider and StructureViewModel.ExpandInfoProvider to control tree expansion behavior.
    See Also:
    TreeBasedStructureViewBuilder.createStructureViewModel(Editor), TextEditorBasedStructureViewModel
